[The Astrakhan oblast is a federal subject of the Russian Federation, part of the Southern Federal District. The administrative center and capital is Astrakhan city. This oblast is situated in the Caspian lowland where the Volga River flows into the Caspian Sea. The largest part of Astrakhan region is occupied by semi-desert.

